      <section>
        <title>Shaft lubrication</title>

        <para>The primary shaft lubrication system is electrically driven and
        operates continuously whilst the main engine is running. If the
        automatic lubrication system fails, a conventional manual lubrication
        cup can be used to ensure that the shaft can be operated
        safely.</para>

